@startuml TP_AgentPipeline
left to right direction

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #EEF6EE
skinparam componentBorderColor #5A9E5A
skinparam componentFontSize 10
skinparam nodesep 12
skinparam ranksep 12
skinparam padding 5

' ── Phase 1: Setup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
[START] --> [Describe Business\nActivities]
[Describe Business\nActivities] --> [Write Supply\nChain Overview]

' ── Phase 2: Parallel research + analysis ───────────────────────────────────
[Write Supply\nChain Overview] --> [Industry Research\n(Global & Indonesia)] : Branch A
[Write Supply\nChain Overview] --> [Write Functional\nAnalysis] : Branch B

[Industry Research\n(Global & Indonesia)] --> [Location, Regulations\n& Macro Environment]
[Location, Regulations\n& Macro Environment] --> [JOIN 1]

[Write Functional\nAnalysis] --> [Determine Business\nCharacterization]
[Determine Business\nCharacterization] --> [JOIN 1]

' ── Phase 3: Transaction analysis ───────────────────────────────────────────
[JOIN 1] --> [Write Transaction\nBackground]
[Write Transaction\nBackground] --> [Comparability\nAnalysis]
[Comparability\nAnalysis] --> [Select TP\nMethod (TNMM)]
[Select TP\nMethod (TNMM)] --> [Select\nPLI]

' ── Phase 4: Parallel output ────────────────────────────────────────────────
[Select\nPLI] --> [Write TP\nConclusion] : Branch C
[Select\nPLI] --> [Write P/L\nOverview] : Branch D
[Select\nPLI] --> [Research Comparable\nCompanies] : Branch E

[Write TP\nConclusion] --> [JOIN 2]
[Write P/L\nOverview] --> [JOIN 2]
[Research Comparable\nCompanies] --> [JOIN 2]

' ── Phase 5: Summary ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
[JOIN 2] --> [Write Executive\nSummary]
[Write Executive\nSummary] --> [END]

@enduml
